<br>
One tip I have for anyone doing this: Unless you're a twink, don't even TRY this in the mid 20s--the MoB is in every way except con a level 30 MOB, even though it cons even/blue at 25. Don't try to cast on it at 25, it'll partially resist Ward Undead 80% of the time, and fully resist 10% of the time. Not to mention, root breaks early, so root/heal doesn't work well. They both aggro as soon as you enter the room, as well. The drop rate seems about... 5%, MAYBE 10%. <br>
<br>
